{"tid":945613,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"強國肥閪火車一人霸三個位瞓 被拘留5日","createTime":"2018-12-18T04:36:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-18T07:40:25.000Z","uid":75969,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3a021bd2ec3bd3b48b52affa11d69902fb29c483","tid":945613,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T04:36:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20181218/_2018121811015411868.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20181218%2F_2018121811015411868.jpg&h=928af6f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對於火車及高鐵霸位的事件，雖然已經提高了執法，但仍屢見不鮮。近日，吉林至瀋陽的火車上，一名身材肥大的劉姓女子，一人佔三座位躺着睡覺，面對乘警還稱「別跟我整這些沒用的」。多次警告無效，到終點站後警方強制帶走劉女。最終劉女被行拘5日。<br />\n<br />\n據報，事發在上周五（14日）16時35分，吉林至瀋陽的K7426次列車從撫順北站開車後，乘警接到報案，稱3號車廂有旅客霸佔他人座位，乘警隨即趕到現場。<br />\n<br />\n經了解，「霸位」旅客劉某手持該次列車4號車廂98號座位的車票，上車後她卻來到3號車廂，躺在了85、86、87號座位上睡覺。這三個座位的旅客要求劉某讓出，但劉某不理不睬，繼續躺在座位上。<br />\n<br />\n列車長勸說無效後，只好向乘警報案。乘警了解事實後，當場告知劉某的行為已經擾亂了列車秩序，但劉某態度十分蠻橫，不但不讓出座位，還以種種理由拒不配合警方工作。在多次警告無果後，乘警聯繫瀋陽車站派出所，在列車終到瀋陽站後，將劉某強行帶走，並處行政拘留5天的處分。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/890596\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F890596&d=80JSO3C4DhQkSCqIxZi%2BV54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=c6aa41b2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F890596&h=ac9ef99c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/890596</a>"},{"pid":"e61ff689636b4f65c0761be29b52437a45c8004c","tid":945613,"uid":142279,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T04:37:57.000Z","msg":"諗咗一諗咩係肥閪火車<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"814a285a31589384452e1a1dcea57e257a20adb0","tid":945613,"uid":133529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T04:42:06.000Z","msg":"@肥絲大隻"},{"pid":"413a99965dc396898ef3e494433f949e9cee1fd0","tid":945613,"uid":88628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T04:47:33.000Z","msg":"幫下樓主個傻閪老母<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n強國一名肥閪在火車一人霸三個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65560656b629d7e74307c1a464efad0f7b29aef9","tid":945613,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T04:48:30.000Z","msg":"中國火腿"},{"pid":"b6b2ce8fef97ac19557879fe374b9889e49c7a0d","tid":945613,"uid":65854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T04:48:33.000Z","msg":"真係豬嚟 仲要粉紅色"},{"pid":"346571e37849fe3678aa5e1e82d8b87585161201","tid":945613,"uid":175732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T05:09:33.000Z","msg":"#<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#fatc"},{"pid":"3389dfd8c9ebabd73eb17a352bc42f37dd3d15d7","tid":945613,"uid":3549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T05:23:05.000Z","msg":"五花腩🤤 <br />\n拎去煎應該出好多油<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aece51ff8625e471fa7f3ed5e6bcaae6f51d4cc","tid":945613,"uid":35814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T05:25:10.000Z","msg":"順便驗下有冇豬流感<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bb812fd06e2b73be9e9a4430082e69f1ee20e32","tid":945613,"uid":13653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T05:26:59.000Z","msg":"但照俾個肥閪訓足全程 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"8b6e3157fc2422c5c45d70f3336b15fada1628bd","tid":945613,"uid":25560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T05:47:05.000Z","msg":"有冇暫開條女幾碌？"},{"pid":"0d1f1a0093b5036a043660cd988b2d0d5e4a6c17","tid":945613,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8bb812fd06e2b73be9e9a4430082e69f1e